OL,5, The Post Office chairman was sacked    
OL,6, because it "just wasn't working", the  
OL,7, business secretary says.               
OL,9,FKemi Badenoch told the BBC that Henry  
OL,10,FStaunton's departure was about more    
OL,11,Fthan just the Horizon scandal, in the  
OL,12,Fwake of public outcry over the wrongful
OL,13,Fconvictions of sub-postmasters.        
OL,15,FMs Badenoch said she removed him after 
OL,16,Fconcerns about Post Office governance  
OL,17,Fand "the entire business model".       
OL,19,FLabour called on the government to give
OL,20,Fmore specific reasons for its decision.
